result.title: Why are there no tests in the Gym?
result.content: Why can I check tests in the Contests, but cannot do this in the Gym? I find it rather strange. And are the tests used in the Gym different from the tests in the Contests? I am trying to solve a problem from one of the contests, and while my program passes the tests from the Contests, it can't get "Accepted" in the Gym.
